select * from `users` where `id` = 22 limit 1
select `role_id`, `user_id` from `role_users` where `user_id` = 22 and `hasRole` = 1

select `idProjet`, `dateDebut`, `idEtp`, `idFormateur`, `idParticulier`, `dateFin`, `module_name`, `etp_name`, `ville`, `project_status`, `project_description`, `project_type`, DATE_FORMAT(dateDebut, "%M, %Y") AS headDate, `module_image`, `etp_logo`, `etp_initial_name`, `salle_name`, `salle_quartier`, `salle_code_postal`, `ville`, `idCfp_inter`, `modalite`, `total_ht`, `total_ttc`, `idModule`, `project_inter_privacy`, `sub_name`, `idSubContractor`, `idCfp`, `cfp_name` from `v_projet_form` where `headYear` = '2025' and `idFormateur` = 22 order by `dateDebut` asc

select COUNT(documents.idDocument) as document_count from `projets` inner join `dossiers` on `projets`.`idDossier` = `dossiers`.`idDossier` left join `documents` on `dossiers`.`idDossier` = `documents`.`idDossier` where `idProjet` = 165 limit 1

select `idSeance`, `dateSeance`, `heureDebut`, `id_google_seance`, `heureFin`, `idSalle`, `idProjet`, `salle_name`, `salle_quartier`, `project_title`, `project_description`, `idModule`, `module_name`, `ville` from `v_seances` where `idProjet` = 165

select `idFormateur`, `name` as `form_name`, `firstName` as `form_firstname`, `photoForm` as `form_photo`, `initialNameForm` as `form_initial_name` from `v_formateur_cfps` where `idProjet` = 165 group by `idFormateur`, `name`, `firstName`, `photoForm`, `initialNameForm`

select `idEmploye`, `emp_initial_name`, `emp_name`, `emp_firstname`, `emp_email`, `emp_photo`, `emp_matricule`, `emp_phone`, `etp_name` from `v_list_apprenants` where `idProjet` = 165 order by `emp_name` asc
select SEC_TO_TIME(SUM(TIME_TO_SEC(intervalle_raw))) as sumHourSession from `v_seances` where `idProjet` = 165 limit 1
select `idProjet` from `eval_chauds`
select `idProjet`, `idEmploye`, `generalApreciate` from `v_evaluation_alls` where `idProjet` = 165 group by `idProjet`, `idEmploye`
select SUM(generalApreciate) as generalNote from `v_general_note_evaluation` where `idProjet` = 165 limit 1
SELECT employes.idEmploye, employes.idCustomer, customers.idTypeCustomer FROM employes INNER JOIN customers ON employes.idCustomer = customers.idCustomer WHERE idEmploye = 22
select `idEtp`, `etp_name`, `etp_logo`, `etp_initial_name` from `v_projet_cfps` where `idProjet` = 165 and not `idEtp` is null order by `etp_name` asc
select `idRestauration` from `project_restaurations` where `idProjet` = 165
select count(*) as aggregate from `emargements` where `idProjet` = 165
select count(*) as aggregate from `eval_chauds` where `idProjet` = 165
select AVG(avant) as avg_avant, AVG(apres) as avg_apres from `eval_apprenant` where `idProjet` = 165 limit 1
select AVG(avant) as avg_avant, AVG(apres) as avg_apres from `eval_apprenant` where `idProjet` = 165 limit 1
select `idEmploye`, `emp_name`, `emp_firstname`, `emp_photo`, `etp_name` from `v_list_apprenants` where `idProjet` = 165 order by `emp_name` asc
select `idEmploye`, `emp_name`, `emp_firstname`, `emp_photo`, `etp_name` from `v_list_apprenant_inter_added` where `idProjet` = 165 order by `emp_name` asc
select DATE_FORMAT(dateDebut, "%M, %Y") AS headDate from `v_projet_form` where `idFormateur` = 22 group by `headDate` order by `dateDebut` asc
select count(*) as aggregate from `v_projet_form` where `idFormateur` = 22 and `headYear` = '2025'
